'''阿马克新闻社'''（{{lang-en|Amaq News Agency}}，{{lang-ar|وكالة أعماق للأنباء}}）是一家支持恐怖组织“[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]”的通讯社，2014年成立，使用[[阿拉伯语|阿拉伯语]]、[[英语|英语]]、[[法语|法语]]和[[俄语|俄语]]发稿。其新闻报道基本以伊斯兰国武装分子发动袭击的消息为主。该通讯社曾使用[[WordPress|WordPress]]发布自己的新闻（现已被删除），现在则通过各种[[社交媒体|社交媒体]]对外发布消息<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/15/world/middleeast/a-news-agency-with-scoops-directly-from-isis-and-a-veneer-of-objectivity.html|title=A News Agency With Scoops Directly From ISIS, and a Veneer of Objectivity|agency=[[纽约时报|The New York Times]]|author=Rukumini Callimachi|accessdate=2016-07-17|date=2016-01-14|archive-date=2018-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180726012351/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/01/15/world/middleeast/a-news-agency-with-scoops-directly-from-isis-and-a-veneer-of-objectivity.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.aawsat.com/2016/03/article55348927/amaq-247-news-agency-run-isis|title=Amaq – 24/7 News Agency Run by ISIS|agency={{le|Asharq Al-Awsat|Asharq Al-Awsat}}|accessdate=2016-07-17|date=2016-03-26|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160617044035/http://english.aawsat.com/2016/03/article55348927/amaq-247-news-agency-run-isis|archivedate=2016-06-17|df=}}</ref>。该通讯社甚至还推出了在[[Android|Android]]平台上运行的手机[[APP|APP]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.co.uk/islamic-state-fake-version-isis-news-app-amaq-android-spying-its-supporters-1563313|title=Islamic State: Fake version of Isis Amaq news app is spying on its supporters|agency=International Business Times|accessdate=2016-11-17|date=2016-06-02|archive-date=2019-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190414094008/https://www.ibtimes.co.uk/islamic-state-fake-version-isis-news-app-amaq-android-spying-its-supporters-1563313|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

阿瑪克新聞社的創立者[[巴拉‧卡德克|巴拉‧卡德克]]（Baraa Kadek）2017年6月死於美軍空襲<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2017/jun/1/baraa-kadek-head-isis-news-agency-killed-airstrike/ |title=Head of ISIS ‘news agency’ killed in U.S. airstrike》 |publisher=Washington Times |date=2017-06-01 |accessdate=2017-06-03 |archive-date=2017-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170602231200/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2017/jun/1/baraa-kadek-head-isis-news-agency-killed-airstrike/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

